This is only an addition to the email (specifically the email dark mode) CSS, so you need to have the code already in your work skin for this to show up correctly.
You might need to adjust the “min-height” value in the CSS code, in the “#workskin .popup” section, depending on the length of your email. 
Otherwise, if for example you have a really long email, the darkened background will be cut too short.

The HTML code for this one needs to go right after your last text sentence within the email body, as will show the HTML example.
